      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has invited all Members of Parliament to join discussions on forming an all-party government to resolve the current situation in the country.",
        "According to the President\u2019s Media Division (PMD), President Wickremesinghe has made the relevant request in writing this morning."
